---
layout: base.njk
title: Member Dashboard
description: "Member dashboard — I-PACE Owners' Advocacy Group."
permalink: /member/dashboard/
---

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="page-header__eyebrow">Members</p>
    <h1 class="page-header__title">Member Dashboard</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Auth gate: show when NOT logged in -->
    <div data-auth-gate>
      <div class="auth-gate">
        <div class="auth-gate__icon" aria-hidden="true">🔒</div>
        <h2 class="auth-gate__title">Members only</h2>
        <p class="auth-gate__body">
          Sign in or create an account to access the member dashboard.
        </p>
        <div class="cluster" style="justify-content:center;">
          <button class="btn btn--primary" type="button" data-identity-open="signup">Join / Register</button>
          <button class="btn btn--secondary" type="button" data-identity-open="login">Sign in</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Auth content: show when logged in -->
    <div data-auth-content style="display:none;">
      <div class="callout callout--info" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
        <span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">🚧</span>
        <div class="callout__content">
          <p class="callout__title">Dashboard view coming soon</p>
          <p>Join submissions and vehicle basics are now stored server-side. This dashboard
          does not yet read those records back for member display.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom:0;"><strong>Note:</strong> Frontend authentication gating is not
          sufficient for real private data. Future Netlify Functions will verify Identity JWTs
          server-side before serving any sensitive information.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="dashboard-panel">
          <div class="dashboard-panel__header">
            <h2 class="dashboard-panel__title">Your vehicle data</h2>
            <a href="/submit-vehicle-data/" class="btn btn--sm btn--primary">Submit data</a>
          </div>
          <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);">Stored vehicle basics will appear here once the member data API is added.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="dashboard-panel">
          <div class="dashboard-panel__header">
            <h2 class="dashboard-panel__title">Group updates</h2>
          </div>
          <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);">
            Check the <a href="/updates/">Updates page</a> for the latest news.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="dashboard-panel">
          <div class="dashboard-panel__header">
            <h2 class="dashboard-panel__title">Your account</h2>
          </div>
          <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);">
            Manage your details on the <a href="/account/">Account page</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
